#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$
# Superviseur
# Gestion du masque SIPAR2 

$_AFF
If GIMPORT
 Gosub AFF From GSAISIE
Else
 If GMESSAGE <>""
  Gosub ERR From GSAISIE
 Else
  Raz GERR , GZNUM
 Endif
Endif
Return

$HORODAT
Local Date    A_DATE
Local Char    A_HEURE(10) , A_USER(10)
Local Char    A_STAMP(15)
A_DATE  = [09/11/2018]
A_HEURE = "23:06:26"
A_USER  = "DOC"
A_STAMP = "20181109230626"
Return

$TITRES
Return

$CHG_FMT
Case zoncou
 When "NBSPL"
  If [M]NBSPL=0
  Endif
 When "NBPPL"
  If [M]NBPPL=0
  Endif
Endcase
Return

$VISU
Local Integer A_REPONSE
Global Integer GPRE_VIEW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Mask SIPAR2 [SIP2]
Gosub HORODAT
Local Inpbox "SIPAR2" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [SIP2] As [SIM_]
Grizo [SIP2]10
Grizo [SIP2]15
Grizo [SIP2]20
Grizo [SIP2]30
Grizo [SIP2]35
Grizo [SIP2]40
Boxact [SIM_]
Gosub TITRES
Boxinp [SIM_] Using A_REPONSE
Close Local Inpbox [SIM_]
Close Local Mask [SIP2]
Kill GPRE_VIEW
Return

$HARDCOP
Local Integer X1(0..14),X2(0..14),Y1(0..14),Y2(0..14)
X1(1)=1 : X2(1)=112 : Y1(1)=1 : Y2(1)=5
X1(2)=1 : X2(2)=112 : Y1(2)=6 : Y2(2)=7
X1(3)=1 : X2(3)=112 : Y1(3)=8 : Y2(3)=11
X1(5)=1 : X2(5)=56 : Y1(5)=12 : Y2(5)=22
X1(6)=57 : X2(6)=112 : Y1(6)=12 : Y2(6)=22
X1(7)=1 : X2(7)=112 : Y1(7)=23 : Y2(7)=23
Return

$ON_SPLACT
Onevent INIT_AREA Call D_SPLACT(zc) From W1SIPAR2
Return

Subprog D_SPLACT(VALEUR)
Variable Integer VALEUR
If varinit([M]SPLACT,indice)=0
 VALEUR = 1
Endif
